<plot>Two friends meet again in the autumn of their lives. They have not seen each other for years but soon find their renewed friendship put to the test when one of them falls ill and the other loses his newfound love. The city of Rotterdam provides the background for this story, which specifically aims to entertain senior citizens in terms of it's extremely mild humor, general references, themes (widowhood, lost friendships) and the overall age of the lead characters.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?132580</url></doc>
